{
  "name": "ClickIn360 Project Advocacy",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Project Advocacy (post-delivery)\n\n**Triggers (via CRM Event Router):**\n- `project.completed` → send project feedback survey email\n- `project.feedback_received` → guardrail + 24h Wait → Google review (if score ≥ threshold)\n\nEdit **Config: Edit These Values**:\n- `crm_base_url`\n- `google_reviews_url` (match CRM Settings → Google review invitations)\n- `review_score_threshold` (match CRM Settings → Automations → Project stages)\n- `google_review_delay_hours` (default 24 — must match Wait node)\n\n**NOT** the manual CRM Request review button.",
        "height": 360,
        "width": 560,
        "color": 4
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1840,
        80
      ],
      "id": "31349c9d-0598-453b-9481-e8cc93cf4453",
      "name": "INSTRUCTIONS: Project Advocacy"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "f3a8c2d1-4e5b-6a7f-8c9d-0e1f2a3b4c5d",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [
        -1120,
        128
      ],
      "id": "be63cfc7-319f-4267-b27f-6e509def4c8a",
